    <div class="content-text">
     <p class="mb-4 fs-6 fw-normal">
      Our car park, which serves our guests at the Istanbul Fair Center, has a capacity of approximately 3000
              vehicles. Our car park in our fair halls numbered 9-10-11 is a closed car park, the rest is an open car
              park. There are special parking areas in our car park for our disabled guests.
     </p>
     <p>
      Otopark payment booths; are located at the ground floor level within the parking buildings on the open
              floor of the parking lot.
     </p>
     <p>
      Apart from this, there is a payment point at the -1 red floor ring road exit. Payment can be made by cash
              or credit card at the payment booths.
     </p>
     <p>
      There are also automatic payment points where you can pay by credit card or cash at the entrance to the
              main foyer, at the entrance and exit doors of exhibition halls 7-8, and at the exit doors of exhibition
              halls 9-10.
     </p>
     <p>
      Diplomatic corps and official vehicles can use the parking lot free of charge if they submit the necessary
              documents (official vehicle license and institutional identity card, etc.) to our marketing unit.
     </p>
     <p>
      Subscription procedures must be completed within 1 hour after entering the car park.
     </p>
     <p>
      For questions about parking, you can contact the parking office staff at 0 111 111 11 11.
     </p>
     <p class="fw-bold">
      Important Reminder About Parking Lot Usage
     </p>
     <p>
     </p>
     <ul class="ms-3" style="list-style-type: disc;">
